[COLOR=#e64a19][SIZE=4][B]Civ-War Updates[/B][/SIZE][/COLOR]
This past weekend, Civ-War announced that their release date will be the 5th August at 9pm GMT+2, 3pm EDT, and 12pm PDT! Closed beta applications have been closed, but you can still track their progress by [URL='https://discord.gg/5MzwZaB']joining their Discord[/URL]!

[COLOR=#e64a19][SIZE=4][B]Craftathon[/B][/SIZE][/COLOR]

[CENTER][IMG]https://craftathon.org/img/craftathon.png[/IMG][/CENTER]

This past weekend, Shotbow participated in a charity event called [URL='https://craftathon.org']Craftathon[/URL] where the Shotbow and Civ-War teams participated in a panel talking about game design. We answered interview questions on the topic of designing a fun and exciting game, and then proceeded to answer questions and give teasers about Shotbow in general, be sure to check it out [URL='https://youtu.be/uhncL83p0vQ']here[/URL]!

