[COLOR=#e64a19][SIZE=4][B]Mine Theft Auto Updates[/B][/SIZE][/COLOR]
The long-awaited player data merge from the EU region is now here for MTA! Upon joining MTA, you will be forced to choose between their US or EU data. Check it out [URL='https://shotbow.net/forum/threads/mine-theft-auto-player-data-merge.374926/']here[/URL]!

[COLOR=#e64a19][SIZE=4][B]Qubion Updates[/B][/SIZE][/COLOR]
Qubion has recently announced their termination of partnership with Shotbow, you can read more [URL='https://shotbow.net/forum/threads/the-future-of-qubion-and-shotbow.375517/']here[/URL]. We wish them the best of luck in their future endeavours!

